/workspaces/agent-feed/api-server/docs/SPARC-AVI-Worker-Fix.md:1. **Schema Mismatch**: `work_queue.post_id` points to `posts.id` for user posts, but worker tries to load from `feed_items` table
/workspaces/agent-feed/api-server/docs/SPARC-AVI-Worker-Fix.md:2. **Execution Model**: Worker assumes all work is "generate response to feed content", not "execute user task"
/workspaces/agent-feed/api-server/docs/SPARC-AVI-Worker-Fix.md:3. **Task Type Detection**: No mechanism to differentiate between feed response vs user task execution
/workspaces/agent-feed/api-server/docs/SPARC-AVI-Worker-Fix.md:4. **Payload Structure**: Worker payload expects `feedItemId`, but user posts need task instructions
